{"tid":2179591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教局逼老師只談「濫用自由」","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:28:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0cf5cf6897e4d2608c87c999da0faf7a4981a0","tid":2179591,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/PSFWGY5SC5AZJC6VAXCINO2C44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FPSFWGY5SC5AZJC6VAXCINO2C44%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=154fa61a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FPSFWGY5SC5AZJC6VAXCINO2C44%2F&h=899a7c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/PSFWGY5SC5AZJC6VAXCINO2C44/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教局逼老師只談「濫用自由」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z98nYcbiCmdgIPE-j99R-DsSaSo=/802x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YQZDXSK5TVCGJG3WO3K5Z7PCNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ98nYcbiCmdgIPE-j99R-DsSaSo%3D%2F802x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYQZDXSK5TVCGJG3WO3K5Z7PCNE.jpg&h=40c6ad4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿強就燒國旗的情景準備正反答案，惟被要求只保留「有濫用自由」的答案。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】教育局大幅「河蟹」高中通識和初中生活與社會科教科書後，有初中生活與社會科教師接受本報訪問，控訴有教局人員審查其教學簡報時，要求他在討論燒國旗、議員在立法會內掟蕉，以及示威者硬闖諮詢會場的例子時，只能提供「有濫用自由」而不能提供「沒有濫用自由」的參考答案。有教育學者認為，教師有責任教授不同立場觀點，批評教育局「只講政治正確，不講教育專業」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lZruz4VxqPEjuDoxTs13tRMKxmI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGNMDXSLCRE27N53VSNE2ID3AU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlZruz4VxqPEjuDoxTs13tRMKxmI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGNMDXSLCRE27N53VSNE2ID3AU.jpg&h=7a29408a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有教局人員向阿強表示「政府高層唔容許學校咁教」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「𠵱家條線已經變咗」<br />\n<br />\n任教初中生活與社會科的阿強（化名）時表示，今年2至3月間教授「自由與公平」單元時，簡報加入三個取自經送審教科書《朗文生活與社會》的情景，包括「在公眾地方焚燒國旗」、「議員在立法會投擲物品」，以及「示威者在諮詢會中被拒進場，於是硬闖會場撞毀大門」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n以燒國旗情景為例，簡報列出「有濫用自由」的參考答案：「根據法例，焚燒國旗是犯法的。我們不應&hellip;&hellip;」；至於答「沒有濫用自由」的參考答案，則是「示威者可能只是視焚燒國旗為一種發表意見的方式&hellip;&hellip;這並不代表他們不尊重國家&hellip;&hellip;」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n惟教局人員審視後，建議阿強只保留「有濫用自由」的答案，更明言「𠵱家條線已經變咗」，指「政府高層已經下令，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教大教育政策與領導學系客席副教授梁恩榮認為，教師應堅守專業守則，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教育局回應稱，教師施教時須明確向學生指出焚燒國旗屬違法行為，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3764aacc8dfe55c0a01d67b1c22cf6bae1f87031","tid":2179591,"uid":266336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲唔識上網學野嘅人都。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cea9eaea96433428d6113c3b01bc148ceb5f81","tid":2179591,"uid":254594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"唔係濫用自由<br />\n係濫用權力<br />\n燒國旗根本無損公眾利益<br />\n係箝制自由"},{"pid":"15ff05c2d375653d26014264f8da9a1f4af58a95","tid":2179591,"uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"可教育工作者可以點反抗?"},{"pid":"83e744f62c8f31586897ad5f078678b8c19bb63d","tid":2179591,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:45:55.000Z","msg":"洗腦，下一代好慘"},{"pid":"d903fb1c19fa01e163d5664d773f0dffd3843f19","tid":2179591,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"啲老師又會咁聽話"},{"pid":"55c326dad3675241f6e6f57effadf406727dff35","tid":2179591,"uid":4024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1348d319ee23168